      <title>养老院在为患者接种新冠疫苗方面落后</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/03/nx-s1-5021811/peak-covid-vaccine-nursing-home-patients-low-rate-fewer-than-half-summer-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[COVID-19 继续威胁着美国各地的养老院，但一份新报告显示，自去年秋天以来，只有十分之四的养老院居民接种了最新的 COVID 疫苗。]]></description>
